title: Account Executive/Sr Account Executive - FSU - College Sports
text: The Sponsorship Sales Executive will be responsible for all aspects of corporate sponsorship sales.   Since your site launched in 2000, WorkInSports.com has been the go to place for USA Baseball when we are looking to fill full-time openings and internships. Your reputation throughout the sports industry as a vital tool for job seekers and employers is well deserved. Thanks again! David Perkins
